{"tid":448727,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"「神奇女俠」的煩惱！女神 Gal Gadot 曾認真考慮轉行","createTime":"2017-10-26T13:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T14:42:45.000Z","uid":52215,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cfd181a8165d58b4f38632659fcf530e8ccedd0b","tid":448727,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T13:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/210022_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F210022_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=48944b07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/210028_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F210028_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6eb2f008&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/210033_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F210033_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=01ba5f48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為《神奇女俠》（Wonder Women）這部電影，令全世界都認識到女神 Gal Gadot 的魅力。但事實上，在成名以前她在演藝圈的發展一直都不太順利。2010 年出道的她拍攝過的電影屈指可數，比較令人有印象的作品只得《狂野時速》（Fast &amp; Furious）系列，這樣的境況維持多年以後，更令她一度想放棄一切、回到家鄉以色列。<br />\n<br />\nGal 近日接受外媒《Glamour》訪問時透露：「在我接拍《神奇女俠》以前，我曾認真考慮過收拾一切回到以色列，不再回來洛杉磯。可能在當地當個演員，或是上大學，試試其他事情。」<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n被問到何解會有這樣的「衝動」？Gal 剖白：「你被邀請到這裡試鏡，再進行第二次面試；然後又被叫到另一個地方試鏡。面對鏡頭，聽著別人跟你說成功的話生活會從此改變，但『成功』從來沒有降臨在你身上⋯⋯然後我知道自己已經快要受不了！我還有跟我同行的老公和女兒，老公在以色列當地有很多的工作，這也對我構成很大的壓力。」<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n而正當 Gal 差不多要下決定回到家鄉時，她得到了《神奇女俠》的 offer。就如那位導演所說的：「成功的話生活會從此改變。」，現在她已經是全球公認的女神，電影接過不停，身價暴升，再也不會出現薪酬過低的問題了！<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n另外，Gal 將會再以「神奇女俠」的姿態，現身於 11 月 16 日上映的新電影－《正義聯盟》（Justice League）。"},{"pid":"fec530457663b9f8a6273a36442b970474145a67","tid":448727,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T13:04:57.000Z","msg":"Gal Gadot<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a2794e1ea1ce69a463cebaad5b0afb73dd5b34","tid":448727,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T13:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40047551015fd5ef38062e0a69fa8f64547f3ba","tid":448727,"uid":60588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T13:37:13.000Z","msg":"要不是Zack Snyder"},{"pid":"4c181adc4c02c1fa9aebbf11f5543ddd6c9799d1","tid":448727,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T13:59:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要不是Zack Snyder</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d8ed8f5c59d773b107aa24f37b006a5d252d76","tid":448727,"uid":49392,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T14:08:15.000Z","msg":"個老公做地產，兩個女仲細<br />\n真係做唔做都得"},{"pid":"7cef10a3cd11965da51a99f6da8e142bd9e775ff","tid":448727,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T14:21:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個老公做地產，兩個女仲細<br />\n真係做唔做都得</blockquote><br />\nYaron Versano好撚有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ae3ec2bd0dbe4d051560d53f5f5ad06d1fb673","tid":448727,"uid":3549,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T14:24:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個老公做地產，兩個女仲細<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">真係做唔做都得</span></blockquote><br />\nYaron V